    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Delve into the dungeon</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024960/extras/cbc4abc88e0c3010bf4ac6193624ec18.avif?t=1763336972\" width=576 height=1022 /></span><br>A deep dungeon awaits your exploration. Extreme landscapes, dangerous creatures, treasures, and death.<br>What you will find in the never-ending abyss?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Various items to help your exploration</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024960/extras/2e7ab1816aa14603890e461fd05d0fce.avif?t=1763336972\" width=576 height=1022 /></span><br>Find new items in the dungeon and equip them on your next journey. Find the best loadout and conquer the dungeon.<br>Any items equipped upon death are lost.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ever changing Environment</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024960/extras/fcf23624bf610ef0831abd1780130fbf.avif?t=1763336972\" width=576 height=1022 /></span><br>The deeper you dive, the harsher the environment will be. The patterns you learned, the techniques you acquired may not be feasible in the next stages of the abyss.<br>Learn to survive the new environment, or return home before you see your demise? If you take the risk or not is solely up to you.",
